data_imputer:
AllImputation(categ_cols=['BuildingType', 'PrimaryPropertyType',
                          'LargestPropertyUseType',
                          'SecondLargestPropertyUseType',
                          'ThirdLargestPropertyUseType'],
              missforest=False,
              sk_object=KNNImputer(add_indicator=False, copy=True,
                                   metric='nan_euclidean', missing_values=nan,
                                   n_neighbors=37, weights='distance'))

             seed=None, silent=None, subsample=0.96, verbosity=1)
